<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<h1><%= @application.student.name %> 's Application Decision</h1>
<p>
  Dear <%= @application.student.name %>,
  <br>
  Thank you for your application to <%= @application.university.name %>'s <%= @application.department.name %> program.
  We regret to inform you that we are unable to offer you a spot in our program. We wish you the best of luck
  in your future endeavors.
  <br>
</p>
<p>
  Sincerely,<br>
  The admissions department at <%= @application.university.name %></p>
</body>
</html>
